title: Go To Gym
description: a big head caricature with a tiny body of an Indonesian beautiful chubby girl wearing , grey-white stripe shirt, and grey long pant, white converse, featuring an extremely large nose as the focal point, she stands in a center-body pose, facing the camera with confidence and vigor. The gym atmosphere adds to the sense of depth and movement. The reflections from the mirror illuminate her face and figure without overexposing them. Soft shadows and highlights sculpt her figure, making her a clear focus. Natural makeup with soft pink tones and glowing skin makes her look fresh and clean. The pose is designed. It features a twisted waist and side over the shoulder silhouette, adding both elegance and lively energy, perfect for sporty photoshoots. In a colored pencil style
